      <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mt-4">Speed and load values represent typical ranges from Hytrol, Interroll, and Dematic product lines. Actual capacity depends on roller diameter, pitch, bearing type, and frame gauge. See the <a href="/resources/conveyor-cost-guide/" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-hover font-semibold">cost guide</a> for pricing details.</p>
